Method Body

1) Method body starts with opening curly braces '{' and closing curly braces '}'. 
2) All statement of method goes within the pair of curly braces
3) Execution of method stops on either 'return' statement or closing curly braces'}'
4) e.g. 
public int go(int x, int y)
{
 int sum = x + y;
 return sum;
}